---
title: Sweet Umami Pork Burgers with Katsu Mayo & Crunchy Sesame Almond Salad
description: Juicy pork patties, crisp lettuce, fluffy buns and all the flavor you can handle—from the scallions in the patty, to the savory-sweet umami-packed katsu sauce on top, to the crisp sesame-dressed green salad with nutty almonds served on the side. If you’re ready to change up your burger game for a fresh, innovative spin, this one’s for you!
